The source rpm for this comes from
    https://copr.fedorainfracloud.org/coprs/boeroboy/hashicorp/
The actual download location varies but if you install the yum repo
    https://copr.fedorainfracloud.org/coprs/boeroboy/hashicorp/repo/epel-7/boeroboy-hashicorp-epel-7.repo
and run
    yumdownloader --enablerepo=copr:copr.fedorainfracloud.org:boeroboy:hashicorp --source vault
then you'll download the latest source rpm.
